fantastic shareholder value” the smurfit kappa group operates in  countries  in europe and  in the americas an integrated producer the group has around  employees and sales last year were euro  billion  billion before joining the jefferson smurfit group in  mcgann was group ceo of aer lingus ceo of gilbeys of ireland and prior to that group financial controller of ericsson ireland mcgann is chairman of aon ireland is a director of united drug plc a director of ibec irish business and employers’ confederation and a director of the ucd michael smurfit graduate business school he is also a member of the ert european round table of industrialists and the incoming chairman of cepi confederation of european paper industries risi organizes four regional ceo awards each year in europe asia latin america and north america which are handed out to the winners at the regional risi conferences risi also presents the global ceo of the year award during the annual ppi awards event previous european ceo of the year winners are peter oswald mondi europe  international in  miles roberts ds smith in  jussi pesonen upm in  jouko karvinen stora enso in  christian rynningtønnesen of norske skog in  jouko karvinen stora enso in  and upm’s jussi pesonen in   for press enquiries please contact caitlin howe marketing specialist o  e eventsrisicom notes to editors about the european pulp and paper outlook conference wwwrisicomeuroconf the sixteenth risi european pulp and paper outlook conference will be held at the marriott prague hotel in the czech republic on march   the conference will address some of the key issues facing the european pulp and paper industry more information regarding the conference program and registration details can be found at wwwrisicomeuroconf about smurfit kappa wwwsmurfitkappacom smurfit kappa is one of the leading producers of paperbased packaging in the world with around  employees in approximately  production sites across  countries and with a sales revenue of euro  billion  billion in  smurfit kappa headquarters are in dublin with regional headquarters in paris europe and miami the americas about risi wwwrisicom risi is the leading information provider for the global forest products industry the company works with clients in the pulp and paper wood products timber biomass tissue nonwovens printing and publishing industries to help them make better decisions headquartered in boston massachusetts risi operates additional offices throughout north and south america europe and asia about risiabout risi executive team press releases careers partners resources risi sales  support live chat contact sales  united states  other regions upcoming events aug  risi latin american conference  august     são paulo brazil sep  ppi transport symposium  september     savannah usa oct  tissue  october     miami usa view all about risi risi generates the most trusted content on global forest products and related markets learn more back to top speak with a sales representative now contact sales × risi sales  support contact sales  united states  other regions amanda lippert menu dead work awards the a’s dead work awards was a juried awards ceremony that showcased the work — submitted by various philadelphia advertising agencies — which never lived to see the light of day the event was held afterhours at the mütter museum a venue with an extensive collection of medical oddities which inspired the visual concept and use of glowinthedark ink for this promotional posterscreenprinted in silver and glowinthedark ink on black paper agency allen  gerritsenrole in project concept development and designcreative direction ryan johnson the essence of racing as a sponsor of nascar indycar and the nhra sunoco wanted to stake their claim as the official fuel of motorsports in the united states when it comes to race day sunoco is what makes burning rubber possible we wanted to tell this story in an unexpected lightduring the biggest race at the very start of